  "description": "The \"youthful bookstore comedy\" revolves around the folks who work in a manga shop deep in a certain \"Electric Town\" neighborhood. (\"Denki-Gai\" or \"Electric Town\" is a popular name for shopping areas that specialize or used to specialize in electric and electronic items, like Tokyo's Akihabara.) The protagonist Umio works part-time at \"BOOKS Umanohone\" along with his senior at work (but not in age) Hiotan. As many dedicated manga fans visit the store, there is always something going on.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)",
